file.name: allof_ref_inline_inline.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: CC-20717 test - OAS3
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /something:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: ok
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Bar'
components:
  schemas:
    Foo:
      type: object
      properties:
        foo:
          type: string
    Bar:
      type: object
      properties:
        foo1:
          description: An instance of Foo
          allOf:
            - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
        foo2:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
    OneOfTest:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Foo"
        - type: object
          properties:
            foo:
              type: string
    SchemaTest:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/OneOfTest'
        - type: object
          properties:
            schemaTestInline1Foo:
              type: string
            schemaTestInline1Ref:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Bar'
        - type: object
          properties:
            schemaTestInline2Foo:
              type: string
            schemaTestInline2Ref:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Bar'
